title: Fertility Workshop
desc:
Join us for an afternoon of exploration and education as we balance the hormones and nervous system with a nourishing yin yoga practice, and an enlightening conversation about spine health and nutrition to support optimal physical, emotional and energetic wellness. 
 Our fertility workshop will be presented by Alana Kessler,?MS RD CYT, Ayurveda Specialist and?Dr Megan Hondru DC, a holistic chiropractor. 
   
 Sunday, December 13  
 2:30 - 5pm
